title: Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000: Device information
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/vertiv
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Reports basic identification of a Vertiv Avocent ACS 8000 console server:
 host name, product model, part number, serial number, bootcode version
 and firmware version. The check always reports OK and is intended as a
 static information service.

 The section also sets two host labels:
 {cmk/vendor:vertiv} and {cmk/device_type:console_server},
 plus {vertiv/model:<model>} so other rules can target ACS hosts.

inventory:
 One service per host is created.
